Greece to Reduce Wages for 30,000 State Workers, Official Says

-- B y   E l e n i   C h r e p a
-- 
2011-09-21T16:35:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/greece-to-reduce-wages-for-30-000-state-workers-official-says.html
Greece  plans to put 30,000 state
employees in a labor reserve system at reduced wages to cut
spending this year, said a government official who declined to
be named.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eleni Chrepa in Athens at 
